{"tid":1557971,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"我今日食咗加藤屋啦，你呢","createTime":"2019-09-10T10:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T14:05:39.000Z","uid":202895,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0269cf6b41f3ca86d2c52d0ce6a2c76ef4f8b8fb","tid":1557971,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gw4aGCL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgw4aGCL.jpg&h=18175bd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加藤屋真係好正啊<br />\n今日去都幾多人下，姐姐做到冇停手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食咗個鐵板麻辣牛肉飯<br />\n我就叫咗中辣嘅，入口都覺得夠麻，正<br />\n但係可能多人嘅關係，油落得幾重手下<br />\n連汽水50蚊，唔洗再去pepper lunch啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地食咗未啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91332fdcefb372b218aed41fe30c2b7d542547d6","tid":1557971,"uid":113525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:08:57.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n<br />\n利申食左 麻辣牛肉飯"},{"pid":"6035f676794f23cb5c4164c4855a8b52598463f9","tid":1557971,"uid":33769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:09:13.000Z","msg":"上個禮拜食咗，大份得濟<br />\n食唔哂"},{"pid":"f875ba74bdbaff803a9e6bc7c83ccb02b1946243","tid":1557971,"uid":97863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:09:46.000Z","msg":"末呀，將會去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f429f8e7cbff2b326ce6d98a3e7f187dc191ac","tid":1557971,"uid":264717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cfvEzY8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcfvEzY8.jpg&h=0ece20a4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gjkhmD8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgjkhmD8.jpg&h=ca9a0731&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"908f8e1423f7801c9389aedc1